         This configuration continues SNAP sync testing from run 005.
         
         Run 006 Purpose:
         - SNAP sync is the UNIT UNDER TEST
         - Focus on SNAP protocol implementation validation
         - Capture detailed logs of capability exchange and SNAP message flows
         - Suppress non-SNAP-related logging to reduce noise
         
         Run 005 Observations:
         - SNAP sync made zero progress
         - All GetAccountRange requests timed out with no responses
         - ETC mainnet peers only advertise ETH68, not snap/1
         - Need detailed logs to analyze the capability negotiation flow
         
         Changes in run 006:
         - SNAP sync ENABLED (unit under test)
         - FastSync DISABLED (isolate SNAP behavior)
